There are 5 key modules in the Snd product of the comviva

1. Channel Management  -> handles channel creation and target allocation  (manages channel lifecycle)

2. Inventory Management  -> inventory pricing and price allocation (manages inventoey movement in the sales chain)

3. Warehouse Management  -> warehouse creation and it is a hierarchy management (manages distribution backbone)

4. Dealer Management  -> target view and tracking  (manages mass retail channel that do the tertiary sales)

5. Comission Management  -> target creation  (for defining the comission rules and events)
